                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1194612662" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1194612662">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/155619487/">loveisatouch</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">非常喜歡看我國的歷史，特別是野史，津津有味。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1153257840">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1153257840" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1153257840" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1153257840">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/41519556/">moonshy</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-02-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">有点像张中行先生的《负暄琐话》系列，写民国时期的逸闻轶事，短小丰富，用语饱满，由此可以窥见民国时候的风物精神，人文风气，独立个性，仿佛隔空细数各种人、事的脉络，有趣有回味。推荐！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
